OL,3,CFive-year-old train superfan given
OL,4,Cchance to be driver for day
OL,6,FA five-year-old train lover has
OL,7,Fenjoyed a dream come true experience
OL,8,Fbecoming a rookie train driver for a
OL,9,Fday.
OL,11,FDaniel Rogerson, from Standish, Wigan,
OL,12,Fwas surprised with a trip to attend
OL,13,FAvanti West Coast's driving school
OL,14,Fafter the operator heard about his
OL,15,Flove of Pendolino trains.
OL,17,FThe little boy was given the chance to
OL,18,Fsit in a driver's cab, had a behind-
OL,19,Fthe-scenes tour of Crewe station and
OL,20,Fwas taught how to dispatch a train.
