OL,3,CFive-year-old train superfan given
OL,4,Cchance to be driver for day
OL,6,FDaniel's passion started when he was
OL,7,Fgiven a wooden train track when he was
OL,8,Fjust one year old. It has expanded and
OL,9,Fnow fills the family's living room.
OL,11,FDaniel's mum, Elaine Rogerson, said:
OL,12,F"Daniel loves to watch trains `
OL,13,Fwhether it's from the nearby train
OL,14,Fbridge or on YouTube.
OL,16,F"So, being given the opportunity to
OL,17,Fbecome a rookie train driver was
OL,18,Famazing! It's an experience we'll
OL,19,Fnever forget.
