OL,3,CFive-year-old train superfan given
OL,4,Cchance to be driver for day
OL,6,F"After his time at Avanti West Coast's
OL,7,Fdriving school, I couldn't be more
OL,8,Fcertain he's destined to be a train
OL,9,Fdriver."
OL,11,FWhen Daniel isn't playing with his
OL,12,Fcherished railway track, he enjoys
OL,13,Ftrain spotting and spends hours with
OL,14,Fhis grandad seeing the trains pass
OL,15,Fthrough his local station.
