OL,3,CFive-year-old train superfan given
OL,4,Cchance to be driver for day
OL,6,FBut it is Daniel's love of riding on a
OL,7,FPendolino that is his favourite
OL,8,Factivity ` with his mum regularly
OL,9,Faccompanying him on rail trips between
OL,10,FWigan and Lancaster, so he can
OL,11,Fexperience the high-speed journeys for
OL,12,Fhimself.
OL,14,FHe even has a bed which has been
OL,15,Fspecially made in the shape of a
OL,16,FPendolino.
