OL,6,FIt was a photo of the bed spotted by
OL,7,Fthe train operator on social media
OL,8,Fwhich prompted them to invite the
OL,9,Fsuperfan to become a train driver for
OL,10,Fthe day.
OL,12,FNatalie Whitehouse, Head of Learning
OL,13,Fand Development at Avanti West Coast,
OL,14,Fsaid: "We had a great time welcoming
OL,15,FDaniel to our driving school for the
OL,16,Fday.
